  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "‘Bradley Headstone!’"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "‘I’ve got it now!’ said Riderhood, after attentively listening, and internally repeating: ‘Bradley. I see. Chris’en name, Bradley sim’lar to Roger which is my own. Eh? Fam’ly name, Headstone, sim’lar to Riderhood which is my own. Eh?’"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "Shrill chorus. ‘Yes!’"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
