  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "With a half glance around him at his pupils, Bradley returned:"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "‘Do you suppose he is here?’"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
    "innerHtml": "‘Begging your pardon, learned governor, and by your leave,’ said Riderhood, with a laugh, ‘how could I suppose he’s here, when there’s nobody here but you, and me, and these young lambs wot you’re a learning on? But he is most excellent company, that man, and I want him to come and see me at my Lock, up the river.’"
  },
  {
    "tag": "p",
